data.name: Level Resist Wall
data.desc: If a monster(s) you control is destroyed by battle or an opponent's card effect: Target 1 of those monsters; Special Summon monster(s) from your Deck in Defense Position so their combined Levels equal the Level of that monster, but negate their effects. You can only activate 1 "Level Resist Wall" per turn.

card_sets.set_name: Egyptian God Deck: Obelisk the Tormentor
